In contrast, while Idea 0 (XTabRobust) proposes "cross-component dependency strength," it remains a scored attribute without a formal graph-based modeling of dependencies. Thus, Idea 1 offers a more principled, scalable, and theoretically grounded framework that pushes beyond current literature.

